title: Poser Target View Chris II
description:
Link : http://marketplace.target-view.nl/products/Chris-II.html

Chris II is a strong male character specially designed for Comics and Games 
With his tiny head, large Torso and long legs, he has the typical Comic characteristics 
Give your scenes, that little extra with adding this amazing Guy.

Right as we speak over more than 100 morphs allready in this amazing character
Advaned Skeleton
Use the scales of Chris II to create cartoony affects
Wardrobe Wizard Compatible
Get a license at PhilC Designs 
Now Daz Studio 4.6 native figure files included.
Texture resolution 2048*2048 TGA

Additional notes

Set Skinning to traditional skinning for the show hide files to work.
Then set back to unimesh, now select a bodypart and make it invisible and visible,
all the parts that were made invisible by the Hide - Unhide files will now be invisible.

Products needed :
Smith Micro Poser 2014
Daz Studio 4.6

Recommended :: The Invisible Man

1 zipfile : 12.1 mb
